  "title": "Staff Nurse – Entry Level | Hospital",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver safe, effective, and holistic nursing care to patients.</li>\n  <li>Monitor and document vital signs, symptoms, and overall health status.</li>\n  <li>Accurately maintain patient records.</li>\n  <li>Participate in ward rounds, shift handovers.</li>\n  <li>Support and mentor junior staff and student nurses as needed.</li>\n  <li>Communicate effectively with patients and their families, providing education and emotional support.</li>\n  <li>Address patient queries and concerns empathetically and professionally.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma/ Degree in Nursing</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid SNB</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduates/ entry level candidates are welcome.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
